backgroundInformationList.description: Notice of Passing of By-law 808-2021 - 625 Church Street

noticeDescription: Take notice that the Council of the City of Toronto has passed By-law 808-2021 to designate the property at 625 Church Street (Ward 11 University-Rosedale) as being of cultural heritage value or interest.
